# Portfolio-RMichels Overview

- Personal portfolio at [rmichels.com](https://rmichels.com): **Astro** static site (EN root / DE `/de/`).
- Content: markdown collections in `src/content/projects/` and `src/content/projects-de/`.
- Styles: Sass in `src/styles/` (Vite build).
- Client JS: TypeScript islands in `src/islands/` (Three.js, filters, etc.).
- Deploy: GitHub Actions builds `dist/` → FTPS to Hostinger.
- Do not refactor application logic unless explicitly asked.

## Page pattern

```astro
---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const locale = 'en';
---
<BaseLayout title="..." description="..." locale={locale} pageType="about">
  <!-- content -->
</BaseLayout>
```

Subdirectory routes: `src/pages/development/[slug].astro` for in-development projects (e.g. tourguide).

## Slug coupling

Markdown `slug:` frontmatter = `public/assets/img/{slug}.jpg` (hero image). Keep aligned when adding projects.

## Dev commands

```bash
npm run dev      # Astro dev server (port 4321)
npm run build    # Output to dist/
npm run check && npm run test:unit && npm run test:content
```

See `AGENTS.md` for full agent workflow.
